flowchart TD
    classDef edge fill:#1e1e2f,stroke:#4ade80,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff,rx:10px,ry:10px;
    classDef cloud fill:#0f172a,stroke:#3b82f6,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff,rx:10px,ry:10px;
    classDef db fill:#312e81,stroke:#a855f7,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff,rx:10px,ry:10px;
    classDef client fill:#171717,stroke:#f87171,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff,rx:10px,ry:10px;

    subgraph Tier 1: Edge Network
        E[ESP32 Microcontroller]:::edge
        S[LDR Analog Sensor]:::edge
        S -->|Voltages| E
    end

    subgraph Tier 2: Core Intelligences
        API[FastAPI Gateway]:::cloud
        ML[Isolation Forest AI Engine]:::cloud
        DB[(SQLite Database)]:::db
        
        API -->|Predict| ML
        ML -->|Anomaly Score| API
        API -->|Write Alert| DB
    end

    subgraph Tier 3: Client Access
        UI[Next.js Premium Dashboard]:::client
        User[System Administrator]:::client
        
        DB -.->|Read Sync| UI
        UI -->|Display| User
    end

E -->|HTTP POST JSON| API
UI -->|Polling GET| API
